    "visualHierarchy": "Visual hierarchy is established through clear labels, consistent spacing, and the use of dividers between list items.  Important actions, like deleting the account and logging out, are visually distinct and positioned at the bottom of the screen.  The color palette uses neutral colors for most text and backgrounds to maintain clarity and avoids unnecessary visual noise."
